{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require clear signage to warn drivers in advance of yellow box junctions",
        "additional_details": "Many drivers are caught and see these yellow boxes as a way of making money. At least if there is adequate signage, they should help keep traffic flowing smoothly.",
        "background": "Please consider requiring traffic authorities to install signs that are clear for drivers to see prior to meeting yellow box junctions. All cameras are high up & are not seeing what the drivers see as they are not at eye level. At night & when weather is wet, they can be extremely difficult to see.",
